item.title: SoftLayer_Dns_Domain_Registration_Status
item.description: SoftLayer_Dns_Domain_Registration_Status Service Datatype Description SoftLayer_Dns_Domain_Registration_Status models the state of domain name. Here are the following status codes: *“‘Active”’: This domain name is active. *“‘Pending Owner Approval”’: Pending owner approval for completion of transfer. *“‘Pending Admin Review”’: Pending admin review for transfer. *“‘Pending Registry”’: Pending registry for transfer. *“‘Expired”’: Domain name has expired. Local description The description of the domain registration status names. Type: string
